    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Incidence of dyschromatopsia should be elevated in glaucoma compared to a healthy control
      population. However, the actual incidence rate is not investigated.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
